Convert NaN to NA

nan_to_na.Rd

Convert NaN to NA

nan_to_na(x, verbose = FALSE)

Arguments

x

matrix
verbose

TRUE/FALSE

Value

matrix

Examples

file <- download_data('billing16.proteingroups.txt')
invert_subgroups <- c('EM_E', 'BM_E', 'BM_EM')
x <- exprs(read_proteingroups(file, invert_subgroups=invert_subgroups))
